name: 2024 6th International Conference on Software Engineering and Development
content: Accepted papers will be published in the ACM International Conference Proceedings (ISBN: 979-8-4007-1805-2). ICSED 2017&2018&2021&2022 papers have been indexed by EI and Scopus, and ICSED 2023 was successfully held during October 20-22, 2023, all accepted papers will be indexed by EI and Scopus soon(ISBN: 979-8-4007-0946-3).
